Type: Package
Package: SummaryTables
Title: Publication-Ready Summary Tables for Jamovi
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nour Edin", "Darwish", , "nouredindarwish@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-5527-4539"))
Description: A comprehensive module for creating publication-ready summary
    and regression tables in jamovi, powered by gtsummary. 'Summary Table'
    creates classic "Table 1" summaries, including group comparisons with
    automatic statistical testing, effect sizes, and p-value adjustments.
    'Continuous Table' summarizes a single continuous variable across
    multiple categorical variables, including automatic statistical
    testing and p-value adjustments. 'Cross Table' summarizes the
    association between two categorical variables using cross-tabulations,
    including automatic statistical testing. 'Likert Table' summarizes
    Likert scale items. 'Multivariable Regression' fits multivariable
    linear or logistic regression models. 'Univariable Regression' runs
    separate univariable linear or logistic regression models for each
    predictor. Features include 16 languages and pre-built formatting for
    major journals.
